{"id":24507,"date":"2024-01-12T10:01:00","date_gmt":"2024-01-12T04:31:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=24507"},"modified":"2023-04-12T12:52:39","modified_gmt":"2023-04-12T07:22:39","slug":"industrial-bathroom-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/industrial-bathroom-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"5 Industrial Bathroom Designs That Promise An Elegant Makeover!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Industrial-style bathrooms are a choice many millennials opt for. Here are 5 industrial bathroom designs that you must not miss out on!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\u2019re thinking of giving your bathroom a revamp, an industrial bathroom design could be a great choice. The industrial style bathroom has made a comeback in recent years, and is effortlessly transforming the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">interior design<\/a> space for good. Characterised by exposed bricks, pipes, metalwork, and dark colours and raw materials, this style is inspired by the factories and warehouses that emerged after the Industrial Revolution in the West. The interior design scene in the Indian diaspora has evolved over the years, and what we see currently is mostly a mix of modern and industrial. But it still works like a charm in giving an edgy but classy look to spaces.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The thought of an industrial bathroom design itself sounds exciting and must have opened the doors of your imagination. Let\u2019s explore how you can experiment with the industrial style bathroom designs<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Industrial Bathroom Design With Dark Colour Scheme<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A departure from the traditional industrial bathroom design, this industrial themed bathroom is modern in every sense of the word. But it still gives off an industrial feel \u2014 given its dark colour scheme.&nbsp; Colours like grey, black, white and brown are the staples of the industrial style. And this bathroom style uses the perfect combination of white and grey \u2014 it features textured grey wall tiles while the floor tiles, fixtures and cabinets are all white.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The indirect lighting further brings out the wall design and gives it a raw, rustic look.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This bathroom industrial style is ideal for someone looking for\u00a0 darker shades in colour scheme or simply a touch of the vintage in your bathroom while still keeping it modern.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25161929\/industrial-bathroom-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Modern industrial bathroom ideas with dark colours\" class=\"wp-image-24508\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25161929\/industrial-bathroom-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25161929\/industrial-bathroom-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25161929\/industrial-bathroom-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25161929\/industrial-bathroom-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Opt for dark colours with your contemporary industrial bathroom design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Design your bathroom with our end to end home interior solutions\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/06115036\/design-your-bathroom-with-our-end-to-end-home-interior-solutions-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Industrial Bathroom Lighting For A Distinct Swanky Look!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This gorgeous industrial bathroom design features soft grey tiles that give the space a calming and soothing feel right from the outset. The wooden flooring, dark grey cabinet and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/white-bathroom-design-ideas\/\">white bathroom<\/a> fixtures perfectly add to the whole vibe of the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>But what lends this design an industrial look are the stunning pendant lights. Pendant lights are the distinguishing features of the industrial style.&nbsp; They enhance its look and add a bit of extravagance to the space. The black framing around the mirror is another element inspired by the industrial bathroom style.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>All in all, an industrial bathroom design idea like this is great if you\u2019re someone that prefers a minimalist approach and would go for a statement piece in their bathroom \u2014 to bring some change and newness.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25162837\/modern-industrial-bathroom-lighting-works-its-magic.jpg\" alt=\"Industrial style bathroom with stunning pendant lights\" class=\"wp-image-24509\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25162837\/modern-industrial-bathroom-lighting-works-its-magic.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25162837\/modern-industrial-bathroom-lighting-works-its-magic-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25162837\/modern-industrial-bathroom-lighting-works-its-magic-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25162837\/modern-industrial-bathroom-lighting-works-its-magic-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A stunning pendant light adorns this industrial style bathroom design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Sleek, Minimalistic Industrial Bathroom Design For The Youth!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This industrial bathroom design is again an excellent example of its modern industrial style twin. It is contemporary yet features accents inspired by industrial designs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The exposed plumbing, the black large accents and the black matte sink are some of the distinct features in this bathroom industrial style. Moreover, the design is minimalistic and straightforward, which is a trademark of the industrial bathroom style. This design shows that you can choose industrial bathroom furniture while keeping it minimalist and modern.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12124751\/minimalistic-industrial-bathroom-design.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalistic industrial bathroom design with glass partition\" class=\"wp-image-44380\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12124751\/minimalistic-industrial-bathroom-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12124751\/minimalistic-industrial-bathroom-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12124751\/minimalistic-industrial-bathroom-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12124751\/minimalistic-industrial-bathroom-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>An industrial bathroom with low-key minimalist design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Chic And Spacious Modern Industrial Bathroom With Oval Mirrors<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here\u2019s another stunning industrial bathroom design that is sure to tease your style. The double sink, the wooden cabinet, and especially the oval-shaped mirrors instantly catch the eye.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not to forget the wooden stool that acts as a fantastic addition to the bathroom design and plays a fun tease as an over-compensating rustic industrial bathroom design. It\u2019s a great place to keep essentials and gives a unique touch to the room.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>But at the same time, the open space, the vastness of the washroom, the airy feel, and the use of dark colours \u2014 all give it an industrial edge. The taps also have an old-world charm adding to the industrial vibe of this bathroom space. Moreover, this industrial bathroom also features an oversized window, another striking feature of the industrial style.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Given how chic it looks, this bathroom design is perfect for young couples. Even if you live alone, you can recreate this design as per your needs. All in all, a room like this will totally uplift the look of your home and impress friends and folks<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25163633\/chic-and-spacious-industrial-sinks-for-bathrooms.jpg\" alt=\"Industrial chic bathroom with oval mirrors and sinks\" class=\"wp-image-24514\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25163633\/chic-and-spacious-industrial-sinks-for-bathrooms.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25163633\/chic-and-spacious-industrial-sinks-for-bathrooms-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25163633\/chic-and-spacious-industrial-sinks-for-bathrooms-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25163633\/chic-and-spacious-industrial-sinks-for-bathrooms-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>An airy industrial bathroom design that\u2019s functional and sexy<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Industrial Bathroom That Happily Embraces The Greys And Whites<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In today\u2019s time, people rarely give their rooms unfinished and raw looks or choose salvaged materials to create and decorate spaces \u2014 unless that\u2019s their taste. However, a 3D-ish effect is what you\u2019d come across more often than not in AirBnbs, resort style villas and places you owe your heart to! Why not bring the AirBnb vibe home with 3D tiles in darker shades of grey?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to give your bathrooms an industrial touch, you can always opt for darker shades \u2014 without using all the elements of the style and giving your bathrooms an unfinished, retro look.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here, we see that the industrial bathroom is, for the most part, on the modern side. But the dark-grey shower unit \u2014 besides providing an excellent contrast \u2014 gives off the same feel and vibe you would get from an industrial bathroom design. There\u2019s also a light-coloured, wooden door which again gives a raw touch to the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Of course you can opt for darker accents and furnishings to cater to your industrial bathroom design needs, however, a striking contrasting play between greys and whites, never hurt one\u2019s eyes<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25163919\/industrial-style-bathroom-vanity-with-dark-shades.jpg\" alt=\"Industrial style bathroom vanity\" class=\"wp-image-24516\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25163919\/industrial-style-bathroom-vanity-with-dark-shades.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25163919\/industrial-style-bathroom-vanity-with-dark-shades-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25163919\/industrial-style-bathroom-vanity-with-dark-shades-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/25163919\/industrial-style-bathroom-vanity-with-dark-shades-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>dark greys and light colour contrasts strike a flair for this industrial bathroom design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And with that we come to an end to our list of top 5 chic and stunning bathroom design ideas that are notable examples of how you can use the industrial style, or parts of it, to enhance your bathroom space and make it different from the ordinary.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Everyone uses the same basic designs and colours in their bathrooms, but the industrial style will help you bring in an element of newness and oomph to your space. This idea is meant for you if you\u2019re daring, experimental, and want to give your bathroom and home an exciting touch.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>And you need not worry. Our designers at DesignCafe can help you implement these design ideas and bring your love for the vintage to life. You can get in touch with our designers to take things forward today!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the meantime, on the blog:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/small-bathroom-design-ideas\/\">Small bathroom design ideas<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/master-bathroom-ideas\/\">Dreamy modern bathroom design ideas<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Luxurious Modular Interior Design Ide